"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932545-Olympics-2024-Samsung-phone-eBay\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympians have been caught flogging expensive souvenirs online after receiving free phones at theParis 2024 Olympicsthis summer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 9}, {\"ngram\": \"expensive souvenirs\", \"from\": 36, \"to\": 55}, {\"ngram\": \"free phones\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympicsthis summer\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are estimated to be over 17,000 athletes participating at the Games and each athlete was gifted a free Samsung phone on their arrival in the Olympic village.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999937260000844, \"rank\": 6.274038867176159e-06, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"over 17,000 athletes\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 178}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"each athlete\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 222}, {\"ngram\": \"their arrival\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samsung manufactured a limited edition of Galaxy Z Flip 6 phone for the athletes to use while they are in France, which features a gold finish, custom leather case, unique platina and more.\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999937260000844, \"rank\": 6.274038867176159e-06, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.998207265968308, \"rank\": 0.0007345562767593833, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a limited edition\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"Galaxy Z Flip 6 phone\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold finish\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"unique platina\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been exclusively designed for the Olympics 2024 athletes and was not released for the general public to buy, making it a coveted item for fans desperate to get their hands on the latest phone.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics 2024 athletes\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"the general public\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"their hands\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest phone\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Samsung's move - which would have cost them around \\u00a316.3million in potential sales - may have backfired after it emerged several athletes were selling their phones on online auction websites eBay and Marktplaats.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999937260000844, \"rank\": 6.274038867176159e-06, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EBay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"eBay\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EBay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EBay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"potential sales\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"several athletes\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"online auction websites\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"Marktplaats\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Multiple listings can be found of the Samsung phone for sale on the website, and because it is not available to buy anywhere else, athletes have been busy hiking up the price.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999937260000844, \"rank\": 6.274038867176159e-06, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Multiple listings\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"sale\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"the website\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discovery+is\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the new home\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995857252, \"rank\": 4.142335898570109e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The streamer\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"3,800 hours\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999999506276266, \"rank\": 4.937258505127513e-08, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports fans\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a33.99a month\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The listing prices range between \\u00a35,096 ($6,500) and \\u00a37,840 ($10,000), while there are alternatives with a lower starting price - presumably as a method of creating a bidding war.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The listing prices\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"alternatives\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"a lower starting price\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"a method\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"a bidding war\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The normal retail price of a Galaxy Z Flip 6 phone with 512GB storage is \\u00a3955 ($1,219), but the foldable edition of the phone appears to be catching the eye of tech collectors.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The normal retail price\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"a Galaxy Z Flip 6 phone\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"512GB storage\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"the foldable edition\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"the phone\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"the eye\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"tech collectors\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB athletes Duncan Scott, Bejamin Proud, Bryony Page, Oliver Wynne-Griffith and Tom George were all seen taking victory selfies on the podium with their phones on Day 7 of the Olympics after they won their respective events.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9974872486523423, \"rank\": 0.002426774790081991, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9913273362707572, \"rank\": 0.004373974849644039, \"text\": \"Duncan Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bryony Page\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\"}, {\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oliver_Wynne-Griffith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oliver Wynne-Griffith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oliver_Wynne-Griffith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oliver_Wynne-Griffith\"}, {\"begin\": 1810, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_George\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom George\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_George\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bejamin Proud\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"victory selfies\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective events\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it seems some other athletes are keen for a quick boost to their bank accounts by cashing in on the high-tech gadget phone.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some other athletes\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"a quick boost\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"their bank accounts\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"the high-tech gadget phone\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Technically, Olympians are not prohibited from selling the limited edition phones.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"the limited edition phones\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it has reflected badly on the sponsor, who experienced a rise in sales from the use of selfies on the medal podium, that people are keen to offload