"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy The reality is that some athletes will never have a chance to reach the podium, and selling a phone as valuable as the Samsung could contribute to their living costs during the Games and beyond.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999937260000844, \"rank\": 6.274038867176159e-06, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"The reality\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"some athletes\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2955}, {\"ngram\": \"a phone\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"their living costs\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"yo